Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:06.35,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:06.35,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:12.69,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:12.69,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:27.44,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:27.44,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:39.12,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.08,0:00:39.12,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:44.62,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:44.62,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:50.16,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:50.13,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:56.40,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:56.40,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:01.71,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:01:01.71,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:07.41,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:07.41,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.18,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.18,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! They're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:46.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hagu-chan, what is this dish called?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:47.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pump-Mint.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:51.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I arranged mint chocolate ice cream\Non top of a microwaved pumpkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:53.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:03.81,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys don't like pumpkin as it is, and she's stuffing\Nit with something even worse like mint chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:09.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Doesn't this make you feel like you're eating\Nchocolate while brushing your teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:14.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Yamada-san and Hagu-chan always eat things like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:17.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:18.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:22.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll make a great wife, Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, you're embarrassing me, Ayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:30.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. I need to give some to Shuu-chan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:34.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Shuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:36.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please eat a lot and do your best at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:38.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Namu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:43.85,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Namu: {\be1\3c&H000000&}short for {\be0\3c&H635514&}Namuamidabutsu {\be1\3c&H000000&}("I sincerely believe in\NAmitabha"). Roughly equivalent to the Christian "Amen."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:39.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:41.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:43.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is wrong! You're acting like he's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.69,0:02:50.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Please eat a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:56.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan, may I ask what those yellow\Nbits that are mixed in with the rice are?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:03:01.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This is grapefruit-seasoned rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:05.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please pour this boiled whole-apple curry on it and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:10.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you ate food like this all the time, Hanamoto-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:14.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you've always eaten it obediently, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:16.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I respect you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:21.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hanamoto-sensei is so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:23.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been four months already, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mongolia, huh? That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:30.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a man's dream adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:35.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Shuu-chan is eating well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:39.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What if he lost weight because he doesn't like the food over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:41.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sure he's eating fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He might have actually gained weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai! Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:51.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Sensei is doing his best, so you'll\Nhave to work just as hard, Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The school festival is coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:56.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to send him pictures of your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:59.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The school festival, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:05.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll never stand out if you don't make something large.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:10.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I still need to finish three more blueprints and two models.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:13.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Suffer all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:16.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. You're becoming all lax because you've graduated!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You ate it all, Morita-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's asking for seconds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:26.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san, you have the heart of a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:31.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do seventh graders need to attend the school festival, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What else should I make?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:46.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha... Hagu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:49.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:52.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been crying for two weeks straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:53.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:56.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In a way, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:05:01.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamoto, I was an idiot for bringing you along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:04.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:08.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why did we gather tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:11.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a party to show off our cooking skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:12.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it Health-Sports Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:12.59,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Health-Sports Day: {\be1\3c&H000000&}an official holiday in Japan (second Monday of October).
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:19.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself! Want some Pump-Mint?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:26.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to things like this already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:35.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, shall I reveal my special menu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I don't have the ingredients...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:38.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll go buy us a cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:42.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I already have a present!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:45.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you going into my room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Takemoto-kun. It's a present for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:48.45,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\fs34\fscy80\bord2.5\be1\shad0\frz2\move(730,58,724,58)\3c&HE2F0F5&\c&H6D7A80&}10 minutes\Nlater
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:53.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My paints!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:54.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And what in the world is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:56.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The game of Twister...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:05:59.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:04.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, there was something like that, wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:07.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the game of Twister like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Takemoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:12.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the convenience store was open!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:14.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll be a whole cake if we connect all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:14.90,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\bord2\be1\fnAlsina Ultrajada\shad0\fs48\fscy85\fscx105\pos(700,67)\3c&HDCEFFE&\c&H3D5572&}Project
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:14.90,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)\bord2\be1\fnAlsina Ultrajada\shad0\fs48\fscy85\fscx105\3c&HDCEFFE&\pos(163,141)\c&H3D5572&}Outcome
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:16.73,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\bord1\shad0\frz-52\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\pos(364,494)\c&HDDDBDD&\3c&H4A4D51&}Altar Candles
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:16.82,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\bord1\shad0\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy80\frz-37\c&HDDDBDD&\3c&H4A4D51&\pos(385,411)}Altar Candles
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:16.94,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\bord1\shad0\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy80\frz-24\c&HDDDBDD&\3c&H4A4D51&\pos(390,359)}Altar Candles
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:18.82,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\bord1\shad0\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fscy80\frz-13\c&HDDDBDD&\3c&H4A4D51&\pos(392,312)}Altar Candles
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:18.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And here are some candles... these were all I could find.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:20.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:23.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you play Twister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:31.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think two people play by placing their hands and\Nfeet on the colors that are called out in turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:33.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you decide the colors?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:34.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With these!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:37.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I made these and figured we could just draw cards to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:40.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san, aren't there a little too many colors?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:45.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think there's usually just red, blue, yellow, and green.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured the more colors, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we're starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,First, Morita-san on yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:56.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:58.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Takemoto-kun on green.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:06:59.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:01.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, red.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:02.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:04.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue for Takemoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:07.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Purple for Morita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:07.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:11.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Takemoto-kun on pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:11.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:13.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san on orange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:24.93,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}The thing on the moon is two rabbits making rice cakes. Japanese\Npeople think that's what the dark spots on the moon look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:14.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:16.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun on beige.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:17.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:18.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san on ocher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:19.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:21.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun on lapis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:21.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:22.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san on white!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:23.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:24.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun on black!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:25.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:28.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't today my birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:38.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really happy. In fact, I'm pretty depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:39.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada! Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:42.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is painful... Hurry up and tell us the next color!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:46.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada, please hurry and save Takemoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:49.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You might say that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:51.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, pale pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:54.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha. Pale pink. There!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:08:00.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-At this rate, it's going to turn into a\Npenalty game instead of a present!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:05.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Takemoto! I'll help you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:08.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Having this as your memory of your birthday during\Nyour third year of college is too sorrowful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:11.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:15.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't these party games supposed to\Nbe played between guys and girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:19.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you two playing with the birthday boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:21.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, that's a nice idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:26.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're both wearing skirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:29.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a no-go. I wouldn't want my underwear showing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:32.49,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,700)\bord0\shad0\fs46\b0\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\pos(193,59)\c&H5C6459&}Zero Sexiness
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:36.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Takemoto. I couldn't help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada! Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:40.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry with the next color!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:45.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ayu, let's put together a jigsaw puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:47.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's so nostalgic. It's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:49.26,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use the table over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:51.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You two change your minds too quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:53.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:56.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun and I are trying so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:09:00.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two demons abandoning us like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:03.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san, tell us the colors already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:05.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and give him the finishing blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:07.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Takemoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:10.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, I'll end your pain soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:12.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Takemoto, mineral violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:15.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of color is that, anyway?! That's dubious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:18.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Morita-san, moss green!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:21.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, almost! That's permanent green!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:24.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san, it's moss! Moss green!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:26.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:31.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ayu, how does this game end?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:35.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama, how do you end it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:37.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama! Mayama! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:42.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me! Just kill me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:45.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thanks, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:52.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You lose when you can't reach your next color,\Ngive up, or lose your balance and fall down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:53.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:55.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you two hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:57.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You lose when you can't reach your next color, give up—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:59.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care! The next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:09:59.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:03.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The color... The color of their eyes has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:06.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Next, carmine red.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:07.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:08.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Opera!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:13.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-Permanent yellow deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:19.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Passion blue is next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:36.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:39.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:42.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Passion blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:56.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:58.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm not drinking any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:11:00.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:01.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I came on my motor bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:06.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. You ride that thing to work these days, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:09.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't riding all the way to Meguro\Nwith a 50cc engine a little tough?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:13.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's actually really comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:15.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even feel like taking trains anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:19.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your stalking is also a lot easier with a bike, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:24.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san! Don't talk about something\Nthat doesn't exist like you've seen it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:27.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing you, I don't need to see it to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:29.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we're best—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:32.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,frie... nds...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:35.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home since I have to go to work early tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:40.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:41.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:42.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:46.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that once Takemoto wakes up,\Nhe'll carry Morita-san back with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:48.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:49.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:08.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how you're supposed to give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:14.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I just decide to give up and act accordingly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:22.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And move further and further away\Nfrom what my heart really wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:40.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then will I forget everything someday? The scent of his\Nbrown hair, his cold ear, the warmth of his back...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:45.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything, including this pain in my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:48.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:13:02.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a trace... as if nothing was there to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:17.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:21.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That Morita-san... I need to teach him a lesson once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:30.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:39.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All I do is pass by her place every day on the way back from work,\Ntake a break, drink canned cofffee, and wonder if she's doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:41.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm ringing her doorbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:45.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All I do is look up at her room from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:51.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that possibly be stalking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:55.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Oh man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:01.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Although they say that a girl becomes more\Nbeautiful when she falls in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:05.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good for a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:10.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's still working.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:16.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Quietly singing a nostalgic song after brewing coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:23.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she's too far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:32.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:37.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Its boldness, detail, and above all, its huge size!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:42.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that I would be able to see\Nthe birth of two legends at this age!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:45.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, Sensei. You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:51.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With Yamada-kun's graduate thesis and this large bowl...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:54.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...as "The Large Bowl vs. the Large Bowl"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:15:00.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...we will create our department's main exhibit\Nfor the upcoming school festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:02.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, the main exhibit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:05.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To begin with, I'm not an undergraduate here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:08.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use a graduate student's work as the main exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:10.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's okay is okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:13.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I give my permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:15.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada! Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:17.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:20.07,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H263C46&\fad(500,300)\fs56\b0\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\bord0\shad0\an6\pos(284,52)}The two{\c&H213038&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:20.07,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\fs56\b0\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\bord0\shad0\an6\pos(188,87)\c&H555B5C&}are
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:20.07,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H263C46&\fad(500,300)\frz-1\fs56\b0\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\bord0\shad0\an6\pos(160,125)\1c&H6E7779&}chums
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:22.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, what is it at an important time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:25.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:29.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! If it isn't Yamada-kun's mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:31.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:31.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:36.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your family got wiped out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:44.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father, mother, and brother all have\N39 °C fevers and can't get out of bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:41.46,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\shad0\bord0\fs56\b0\frx5\fscy80\fnAlsina Ultrajada\b1\pos(748,57)\c&H3D5D96&}Yamada\N{\fs36}Liquor Store
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:46.43,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H000000&}We are extremely sorry to say this,\Nbut we will be closed today.\N— {\be1\3c&H635514&}The store owners
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.43,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:49.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going home for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:50.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:52.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be alone tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:59.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're lonely, why don't you ask the landlady\Nto have Midori-chan come spend the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:00.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Midori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:04.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a poodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.11,0:16:06.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu, say hello to your papa and mama for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.79,0:16:14.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Hagu-chan. I'll be back tomorrow or the day after!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:13.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye! Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:16.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye! Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow, Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:17.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:19.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:20.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:21.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please make sure to eat dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:21.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:24.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And make sure to lock the patio door!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:25.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:27.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And make sure Midori-chan spends the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:27.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:30.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada-san, you sound like a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:34.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be fine, Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:36.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only for one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She might not look like that, but Hagu-chan is 19 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:44.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'm still worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:50.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, one time my hamster died when I left it for just two days!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:54.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother was there at her deathbed, but\NI couldn't see her before she passed away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:17:00.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Yamada-san... is it really okay to\Nput those two in the same category?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:17:00.38,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\c&H5B5C51&\fs32\b0\fscy70\fnAlsina Ultrajada\shad0\bord2\be1\pos(400,263)\3c&HD3E4E8&}Hamu        Hagu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:17:00.38,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Hamu as in Hamusutaa{\be1\3c&H000000&} - Hamster
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:03.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'm really worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:09.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, at night she calls out for Sensei and cries in her sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:14.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:21.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan seemed to be in high spirits, but her\Nsmall, muddy hands were trembling a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:27.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how important Hanamoto-sensei is to Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:35.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, Hagu-chan is always with\NSensei, whether she's at school or at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:42.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't tonight her first real night alone since she came to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:44.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Her first night alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:50.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:57.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I had no idea what to do, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:03.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! I'm Shinobu. What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:08.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san and the others held a welcome party for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:10.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:15.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no one for Hagu-chan right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:17.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:25.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:26.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:30.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Takemoto-kun! Hold on, I'll open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:34.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:37.93,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\shad2\fscy70\fs40\fnShangri-la\pos(425,49)\c&H01029A&\3c&H000026&\4c&H000026&}Interpretation: {\fs65}  Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who might this lady be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:45.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Midori-chan. Isn't she cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:48.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:53.82,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's right. What am I doing, coming over\Nto a girl's place at night all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:57.33,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\shad2\fscy70\fs40\an6\fnShangri-la\3c&H000026&\4c&H000026&\pos(667,44)\c&H0101AA&}Interpretation:{\fs56} If you try anything funny, I'll fucking kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:57.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun, did you forget something here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:59.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:06.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, I was passing by, and... so... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:11.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want some tea? Or roasted chestnuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:12.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or boiled eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:16.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to put together a jigsaw puzzle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:21.06,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I'm glad I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:22.98,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:33.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:35.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:37.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:39.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please spend the night here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.17,0:19:47.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And please make me a Versailles kitchen set!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:50.59,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it would be something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:52.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay? Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:58.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:00.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll spend the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:09.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:12.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If... If you don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:18.95,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-N-Next time Yamada-san and Sensei aren't around...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:20.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:24.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:30.63,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like she'll break if I touch her even a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:36.22,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but something in my heart is struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:41.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan, where are my souvenirs?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:43.85,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:52.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:56.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you please sleep in your own room?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:59.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to wake up early tomorrow, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:27.94,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}akanai mabuta kosutte mieru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:27.94,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I rub my heavy eyelids to reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:33.07,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}pastel moyou no mirai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:33.07,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}A future in the shape of pastels
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:40.20,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}chiribamerareta kigou o tadoru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:40.20,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I follow the scattered symbols
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:44.29,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}taguri yoseta hyoujou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:44.29,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}As my expressions were pulled in closer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:50.04,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}nee nandakke sagashiteita mono
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:50.04,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Say, what was it that we were looking for again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:53.13,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}are wa soune itsudakke
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.58,0:21:53.13,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}That's right, exactly when were those days
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.09,0:22:00.51,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}bokura ga inryoku ni sakarai nagara deatta koro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:22:00.51,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}When we used to meet, denying the attraction\Nthat was forming between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:06.43,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sore ga waltz no you dane fushigi sa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:06.43,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}It's like a waltz, isn't it? It's quite marveling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:12.65,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sasayaku youna komorebi no kousaten de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:12.65,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}We paint away sceneries
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:18.86,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}futari waltz no youni ne mawari nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:18.86,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}As we waltz and spin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:24.99,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}egaki dashite yuku mono
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:24.99,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}Where the whispering sunlight falls through the trees and meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:34.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: That broach was heavy.
